<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Aspen Woods</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Aspen Woods is administered by the Strathcona Christie Aspen Community Association, along with Strathcona Park and Aspen Wood, and operates public tennis courts, an outdoor hockey and skating rink and a sports/playing field. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The joint community center for the three communities has a gym, commercial kitchen, lounge, meeting rooms, a sound system and an indoor fireplace, as well as a deck with a great view and a loft. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The community association hosts a variety of programs, including sports, fitness, dance, senior programs, and childcare. Westside Recreation Centre has a fitness center and swimming pool open to the public.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">To the southeast of Aspen Woods is the Westhills Shopping Centre, which has a collection of shops, restaurants and medical facilities (dental and doctor clinics and pharmacies) and a multiplex theatre showing the latest releases. Family restaurants are easy to come by, with a Montana’s, Moxie’s Grill and Swiss Chalet, as well as a number of fast food restaurants.</p>
        </div>
